data.description: ASSUMABLE 3.125 FHA LOAN!!  Buyers must qualify and  meet FHA guidelines and restrictions for loan assumption. Luxury  townhome in the heart of Frisco.    This 3 bedroom, 2.5 bath features spacious bedrooms(walk-in closet in primary), granite counters in the full baths, raised ceilings and a large updated kitchen with stainless appliances. While 3 of the bedrooms are upstairs, downstairs has a bonus room, to be used as either a work area or possible 4th bedroom.  The large utility room has plenty of cabinets for storage. You don't have to worry about keeping cool, as both AC units were replaced in 2020.   Relax on the patio or on the 2nd story covered  balcony.   The HOA takes care of lawn maintenance so you can enjoy living near all Frisco has to offer:  Toyota Stadium, Grand Park(coming soon), local shops, restaurants,  the new Frisco library and other entertainment.  This is a great opportunity to live in one of the fastest growing areas in the country.
